We start in command line:

'npm install -g yo generator-kraken bower grunt-cli'

'yo kraken'

and now our project are created!

In our directory folder run terminal and put
'npm install mongodb mongoose connect-flash express-messages'

To start our project in terminal write
'npm start'

Now we create our database. First we need to start MongoDB. In terminal we put 'mongo' and mongo shell will open.
Next we create 'onlineshop' database - write in terminal 'use onlineshop'. After this we create two collection:
db.createCollection('products');  and  db.createCollection('categories');

Next commands:

db.products.insert({title:'Yellow Backpack', description:'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.', category:'Backpack', country:'USA', collect:'Summer 2016', price:'19.99', cover:'1.png'});

db.products.insert({title:'Red Backpack', description:'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.', category:'Backpack', country:'Ukraine', collect:'Winter 2016', price:'14.49', cover:'2.png'});

db.categories.insert({name:'Backpack'});
db.categories.insert({name:'Luggage'});
db.categories.insert({name:'Woman'});
db.categories.insert({name:'Wallet'});
db.categories.insert({name:'Belt'});

And now, in 'Manage Area', if you 'add category' or 'edit||delete product' you can see Error. I don't know why...